column1: Enter the values of the input for Mix Contract
PLEASE FOLLOW THE INSTRUCTIONS::
Input will be updated in <Algo Name>/inp-output/inp-params.txt

Line-1 space seprated 2 values
Line-2 1 values

Sample Input File:

column2: 1. n: # of Threads <Range: 1 to maximum available H/W threads>
2. K: # of Total AUs or Trans <Range: integer >= # Threads>
3. nAccounts: # of Account in Coin Contract <Range: 2 to 2000>
8. λ: if Miner is Maliciois then 1 else 0
